properties.NAME: BR 110 on N239, Pyles Ford Road
properties.DESCRIPTIO: Replace existing concrete slab on stone abutments with precast concrete culvert and wingwalls.  Reconstruct the roadway approaches and place steel guardrail as required. Place riprap to protect the structure from scour.
properties.NOTE2: No funding in amended FY16 TIP

properties.NAME: BR 185 on Oak Ridge Rd over Hyde Run
properties.DESCRIPTIO: This project involves the replacement of one existing corrugated metal pipe with a precast concrete pipe or box culvert. Additional work includes minor reconstruction of the approach roadway, installation of guardrail as needed, and placement of riprap in the stream to prevent scour. The work will be performed under detour with roadway closure.
properties.NOTE2: No funding in amended FY16 TIP

properties.NAME: BR 748, I-95 Wilmington Viaduct
properties.DESCRIPTIO: This project involves the rehabilitation of BR 1748, 748N, and 748S that make up the viaduct carrying I-95 through Wilmington. Work includes replacing joint seals and joint, reconstructing the concrete barriers, patching concrete spalls in the deck and substructure, sealing cracks in the concrete deck and substructure, cleaning and greasing the bearings, and zone painting the steel girders. Work will be performed in phases to maintain traffic.
properties.NOTE2: No funding in amended FY16 TIP

properties.NAME: SR 896 and Bethel Church Rd Interchange
properties.DESCRIPTIO: No description available at this time.
properties.NOTE2: No funding in amended FY16 TIP

properties.NAME: BR 366 on N399 Chesapeake City Road over Guthrie Run
properties.DESCRIPTIO: Replace existing structure with prestressed, precast concrete beams on geo-synthetic earth reinforced abutments. Reconstruct the roadway approaches and place guardrail as required. Place riprap to protect the structure from scour. This project is funded, in part, using Innovative Bridge Research and Deployment (IBRD) program funds.
properties.NOTE2: No funding in amended FY16 TIP

properties.NAME: BR 424 on Old Corbitt Road, East of Odessa
properties.DESCRIPTIO: Replace CMP with pre-stressed concrete beams on a stub abutment.  Raise and reconstruct the approaches to an elevation above normal high tide.  Install guardrail as necessary.  Place riprap as required for scour protection.
properties.NOTE2: No funding in amended FY16 TIP
